<br />
It was laggy, but the lag was intentional. Since the servers slowed things down everyone had like 5 frames per second. I guess this makes sure that everyone has a fair chance to input commands since realtime speeds meant the people closest to the server tended to get their commands responded to faster and more accurately than people farther away.
